Package: fin
Version: 0.6.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Tsiry Sandratraina <tsiry.sndr@rocksky.app>
Homepage: https://github.com/tsirysndr/fin
Depends: libc6, libasound2, mpv
Description: A neon-electric Jellyfin TUI client for mpv & Chromecast
 fin is a Rust TUI + one-shot CLI that talks to your Jellyfin server,
 searches your library, manages playlists, and pushes streams to either
 your local mpv window or any Chromecast on your network. Chromecast
 playback is fully queued — enqueue, play-next, skip, resume, all from
 the terminal.
